Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要下的话  倒是希望能在早上就开始下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  只是觉得雨下得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你没带伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是我疏忽大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要我借你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,借给我  你用什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是二刀流?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我只带了一把伞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要帮老师做事  所以暂时还不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在我完事之后  这时雨应该就会停了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,听说这雨会越下越大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道明天操场还能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我似乎是偏火属性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可能会被人怀疑雨是我的弱点属性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别看我这样  其实我水属性也挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我从来都没有担心过这个方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz331.6\pos(836,405)}这样子啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz329.7\pos(513,501)}师傅、一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾说和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我买了河童雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这颜色真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得抓紧了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,河童?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是你值日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧  内卷要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷你有带伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你带伊万莉一起撑回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有带伞  非常头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在应该还在楼梯口那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒也是  这么大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,武田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,收上来的笔记本我就放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我还要收拾一下东西  就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  那能麻烦你帮忙补充一下粉笔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就在器材室右边那个架子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看来还要花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是香织吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我今天差点迟到  所以忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,人家很可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  瑞瑞你的伞我就借走了哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别随便给我拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我这绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,香织!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉祸不单行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,香织那家伙  居然真带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后我马上来到这里找她  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是泪水呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亚尔希安战记第二章  是和马莉安娜诀别的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,才不对  你这样会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷  你可别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是有水之精灵的加护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,师傅  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学  原来你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真像那两个人会搞出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后为什么你会留下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友把你的伞借走了不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\b0\bord1\shad0\c&H453A38&\move(308,207,348,227)\3c&HFFFFFF&}香织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要和我一起用这把伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,香织  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,打…打扰了…
